Package: PWS
Title: Personal Weather Station
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Mengyi", family = "Gao", email = "m1gao@stanford.edu",role = c("aut", "cre")), person(given = "Xiang",family = "Zhang",email = "x265zhan@stanford.edu", role = c("aut")))
Description: Extract, organize, visualize and model local weather data. User can use this package to compare data at nearby personal weather stations to show microclimate patterns.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.3)
